      "title": "## Overview",
      "content": "This plan outlines a modern, professional website for an AI, Automation, and Digital Marketing company. The site will feature animated visuals, a clear service and product catalog, detailed case studies, resources, pricing information, and a contact/booking integration, all designed with a specific tech-forward aesthetic."
    },
    {
      "id": "key-features",
      "title": "## Key features",
      "content": "- **View Homepage Content**: Displays brand information, animated hero section, services overview, products, industries, case studies, testimonials, and a call to action.\n- **View Product Listing**: Showcases AI agent templates, workflow automations, chatbots, dashboards, and custom tools in a visual grid with hover animations.\n- **View Product Details**: Provides in-depth information for individual product subpages.\n- **Filter Products**: Allows users to filter products by type (e.g., AI agent templates, chatbots).\n- **View Service Listing**: Presents the company's core services including digital marketing, AI agents, workflow automation, and app/web development.\n- **View Service Details**: Offers detailed descriptions for each service.\n- **View Industry Listing**: Displays industries served (e.g., e-commerce, healthcare, finance) using a grid or card layout.\n- **View Industry Details**: Provides specific information relevant to each industry.\n- **View Case Study Listing**: Showcases completed projects with problem-solution-result narratives.\n- **Filter Case Studies**: Allows users to filter case studies by industry.\n- **View Case Study Details**: Presents detailed case study information including charts and ROI.\n- **View Resource Listing**: Displays available resources such as blog posts, guides, webinars, and glossary terms.\n- **View Resource Details**: Shows the full content of a selected resource.\n- **View Pricing Tiers**: Outlines the different service packages, tiered plans, and retainer options.\n- **View Testimonials**: Displays client feedback and endorsements.\n- **Submit Contact Form**: Allows visitors to send inquiries via a contact form.\n- **Book a Consultation**: Integrates a booking system for scheduling appointments.\n- **Subscribe to Newsletter**: Enables users to sign up for email newsletters.\n- **Interact with Chatbot Demo**: Provides a floating chatbot for interactive demonstration."
    },
    {
      "id": "structure",
      "title": "## Structure",
      "content": "- **Homepage**: Features the animated hero section, overview of services, products, industries, case studies, testimonials, and CTA.\n- **Products Page**: Hosts the visual grid of products, with filtering options and links to individual product subpages.\n- **Services Page**: Displays the list of services offered, with links to detailed service pages.\n- **Industries Page**: Presents a grid or cards of industries served, with links to industry-specific details.\n- **Case Studies Page**: Shows the list of case studies, with filtering by industry and links to detailed case study pages.\n- **Resources Page**: Hosts the blog, guides, webinars, and glossary, with links to individual resource content.\n- **Pricing Page**: Displays tiered pricing plans and service/retainer options.\n- **Contact Page**: Includes the contact form, information on global presence, and booking integration."
    }
